TUGAS 2#

  1. Refleksi terhadap Sumbu x

Nilai \(y\) berubah tanda, \(x\) tetap.

\[\begin{split} \begin{bmatrix} 1 & 0 \\ 0 & -1 \end{bmatrix} \end{split}\]

Contoh: Titik \(P(2, 3)\)

\[\begin{split} \begin{bmatrix} 1 & 0 \\ 0 & -1 \end{bmatrix} \begin{bmatrix} 2 \\ 3 \end{bmatrix} = \begin{bmatrix} 2 \\ -3 \end{bmatrix} \Rightarrow P' = (2, -3) \end{split}\]

  1. Refleksi terhadap Sumbu y Nilai \(x\) berubah tanda, \(y\) tetap.

\[\begin{split} \begin{bmatrix} -1 & 0 \\ 0 & 1 \end{bmatrix} \end{split}\]

Contoh: Titik \(P(2, 3) P' = (-2, 3)\)

  1. Refleksi terhadap Garis \(y = x\) Tukar posisi \(x\) dan \(y\).

\[\begin{split} \begin{bmatrix} 0 & 1 \\ 1 & 0 \end{bmatrix} \end{split}\]

Contoh: $$ \begin{bmatrix} 0 & 1 \ 1 & 0 \end{bmatrix} \begin{bmatrix} 2 \ 3 \end{bmatrix}#

\begin{bmatrix} 3 \ 2 \end{bmatrix} \Rightarrow P’ = (3, 2) $$

  1. Refleksi terhadap Garis \(y = -x\) Tukar posisi \(x\) dan \(y\), lalu ubah tanda keduanya.

\[\begin{split} \begin{bmatrix} 0 & -1 \\ -1 & 0 \end{bmatrix} \end{split}\]

Contoh:

\[\begin{split} \begin{bmatrix} 0 & -1 \\ -1 & 0 \end{bmatrix} \begin{bmatrix} 2 \\ 3 \end{bmatrix} = \begin{bmatrix} -3 \\ -2 \end{bmatrix} \Rightarrow P' = (-3, -2) \end{split}\]

  1. Refleksi terhadap Titik Asal (Origin) Negatifkan kedua komponen \(x\) dan \(y\).

\[\begin{split} \begin{bmatrix} -1 & 0 \\ 0 & -1 \end{bmatrix} \end{split}\]

Contoh:

\[\begin{split} \begin{bmatrix} -1 & 0 \\ 0 & -1 \end{bmatrix} \begin{bmatrix} 2 \\ 3 \end{bmatrix} = \begin{bmatrix} -2 \\ -3 \end{bmatrix} \Rightarrow P' = (-2, -3) \end{split}\]

import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

# Titik awal
P = np.array([[2], [3]])

# Matriks refleksi
reflect_x = np.array([[1, 0], [0, -1]])
reflect_y = np.array([[-1, 0], [0, 1]])
reflect_y_eq_x = np.array([[0, 1], [1, 0]])
reflect_y_eq_neg_x = np.array([[0, -1], [-1, 0]])
reflect_origin = np.array([[-1, 0], [0, -1]])

# Fungsi transformasi
def transform(matrix, point):
    return np.dot(matrix, point)

# Hasil transformasi
P_rx = transform(reflect_x, P)
P_ry = transform(reflect_y, P)
P_rxy = transform(reflect_y_eq_x, P)
P_rnxy = transform(reflect_y_eq_neg_x, P)
P_ro = transform(reflect_origin, P)

# Visualisasi
plt.figure(figsize=(8, 8))
plt.axhline(0, color='black')
plt.axvline(0, color='black')
plt.grid(True)
plt.axis('equal')

# Titik dan warnanya
points = {
    "P (asli)": (P, 'blue'),
    "Refleksi x": (P_rx, 'red'),
    "Refleksi y": (P_ry, 'green'),
    "Refleksi y=x": (P_rxy, 'purple'),
    "Refleksi y=-x": (P_rnxy, 'orange'),
    "Refleksi asal": (P_ro, 'brown')
}

for label, (point, color) in points.items():
    x, y = point[0, 0], point[1, 0]
    plt.plot(x, y, 'o', color=color)
    plt.text(x + 0.2, y + 0.2, label, fontsize=9, color=color)

# Tambahkan garis y = x dan y = -x
x_vals = np.linspace(-5, 5, 100)
plt.plot(x_vals, x_vals, '--', color='gray', linewidth=0.8, label='y = x')
plt.plot(x_vals, -x_vals, '--', color='gray', linewidth=0.8, label='y = -x')

plt.title('Transformasi Refleksi Titik (2, 3)')
plt.legend(loc='upper left', bbox_to_anchor=(1, 1))
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
